 "https://www.zhihu.com/question/488583150"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7YWCn53WgOR2EAMaCDcwODU1NjE3IOLssYoGMAw4nwZAB3IJNDg4NTgzMTUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1635574109.3208494", "card_id": "Q_482847465", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 61}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "只会增删改查的计算机专业学生真的不适合做开发吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "Java 面试官问了一些基本知识以及 Spring boot 框架差不多都可以答的上来，当他问我说除了增删改查还会什么，我说思索了一下好像并没有。叫我说自己的优点，我说学习能力和刻苦钻研，然后被嘲。只会增删改查的应届生真的有那么差劲吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a21cb4dfe1b20d7371cc102ec890e4bc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "135 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482847465"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7YWCn53WgOR2EAMaCDY5NTgxMzM2INPDoYkGMAk4uAJACHIJNDgyODQ3NDY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1635574109.3213468", "card_id": "AT_419060511", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从 3 岁看到 12 岁，你不会回答的问题，这套绘本里都讲了！"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作为传承 60 年的科普经典 IP 《十万个为什么》里的「十万」只是一个用来形容数量很多的虚数词，但它却陪伴了一代又一代人的成长。不过真正实实在在的「十万个为什么」就在你身边——你家的孩子是不是也总是每天缠着你问来问去？只要回答了他的第一个问题，就有…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-79ae20b42feb76837b79135928ecaed0.png?source=6a64a727"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "132 万热度"}, "link": {"url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/419060511"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "十万个为什么", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI7YWCn53WgOR2EAcaCTE4MTI1NDUzMiCU7v+KBij5BDCdAUAJWggxMjY3MTY2OXIJNDE5MDYwNTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyAQcIARIDdmlw"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1635574109.3244133", "card_id": "Q_495394013", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 510}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待中南屋发文否认反华，表示已收集好证据报警，将告赛雷话金诽谤？事件后续将如何发展？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "以下为中南屋发文部分内容： 说我们团队和我个人反华，是比杀人越货更大的指控。 《中华人民共和国国家安全法》第二章，第十五条，明确指出「国家防范、制止和依法惩治任何叛国、分裂国家、煽动叛乱、颠覆或者煽动颠覆人民民主专政政权的行为；防范、制止和依法惩治窃取、泄露国家秘密等危害国家安全的行为；防范、制止和依法惩治境外势力的渗透、破坏、颠覆、分裂活动。」 这位博主的意思，是我们做了这法条所指的行为和活动？ 我一开始真的觉得——不会有人相信吧？毕竟，一个人是否反华，肯定是国家有关部门做过调查后，再进行定性啊。怎么可能等到一个网红大 V 、在网络上可以给别人宣判呢？ ... 我也想过「以死鸣冤、引起上层领导人关注」——但是朋友劝我：能去卧底非洲调查象牙贸易、冒死给外国人证明中国人热爱动物保护，怎么能为了证明自己只吃了一碗粉、自己剖开肚子？ 努力调整心情，今天，我们终于收集好了证据，报警了，下一步起诉这位网红博主诽谤。中南屋 Chinahouse：我们被大 V 扣上「反华」帽子并网暴，家人被威胁…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9572f9c8681bdc3fe7cae5ce1b0fc0b6_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "130 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495394013"}}, "attached_info": "ClYI7YWCn53WgOR2EAMaCDcyMzY4NjQ2IJaW8IsGMI4BOIwRQApyCTQ5NTM5NDAxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1635574109.3252387", "card_id": "Q_23081076", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你们是如何看待《乱世佳人》郝思嘉的性格？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "129 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/23081076"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I7YWCn53WgOR2EAMaBzE0MTMzOTgg4qufmQUwBTj3AUALcggyMzA4MTA3NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1635574109.3255222", "card_id": "Q_495436807", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年下半年「教资笔试」10 月 30 日开考，题目难度如何？你考得怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-99b59a5f09856d482324966d300421db_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "124 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://